          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 27 – 32</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose the correct answer.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">27</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>What are we told about Daniel Everett in the first paragraph?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> He has lived among the Pirahã since 1977.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> It took him seven years to learn the Pirahã language.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> No one would publish his research for three decades.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> Studying the Pirahã language is the focus of his work.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. Studying the Pirahã language is the focus of his work.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q27, D</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Arial;\">Daniel Everett</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A段, “Since 1977, the ethnologist Daniel Everett has spent a total of seven years living with the Pirahã and has committed his career to studying their puzzling speech.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到研究Pirahã语是Daniel Everett工作的主要焦点。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">the focus of his work=committed his career</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">28</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Which of the following is the best summary of the second paragraph?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Humans are the only species to be linguistically creative.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> Humans, bees, birds and whales share a characteristic.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Human language is not fully understood by scientists.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> Humans are the only species to use syntax.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. Humans are the only species to be linguistically creative.\r\n</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q28, A</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">the second paragraph</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">B段，“</span>The debate over the Pirahã language goes right to the core of the riddle regarding how Homo sapiens managed to develop vocal communication. Although bees dance, birds sing and whales even sing with syntax*, human language is unique, if only for the reason that it enables humans to piece together never-before-constructed thoughts, and be infinitely imaginativ<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">e</span> <span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">–</span> think of Shakespeare<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">’</span>s plays or Einstein<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">’</span>s theory of relativity<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">第二段主旨句为 “</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Although bees dance, birds sing and whales even sing with syntax*, human language is unique, if only for the reason that it enables humans to piece together never-before constructed thoughts, and be infinitely imaginative...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”。与其他物种相比，人类在语言使用方面拥有的独特创造力。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义词替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Arial;\">imaginative=creative</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">29</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Why does the writer refer to subordinate clauses?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> to criticise the general approach of linguistics\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> to compare two features of the Pirahã language</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> to explain why the Pirahã language is difficult to learn</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> to exemplify an unusual feature of the Pirahã language</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. to exemplify an unusual feature of the Pirahã language</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q29, D</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">subordinate clauses</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">C段, “Linguistics generally focuses on what features all human languages have in common, but the Pirahã language departs from what some academics have long maintained are essential and inalienable features of all human languages. Most of all, it may be unique for not employing subordinate clauses.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">作者用</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">subordinate clauses作为例子</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">来说明Pirahã与其他语言不同。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">30</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>What point does the writer make about the work of Whorf?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> He thought that numbers were common to all human languages.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> His theory might be supported by Everett’s research.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> His research enabled him to find a new life among the Pirahã.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> He predicted that people like the Pirahã would never be found.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. His theory might be supported by Everett’s research.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q30, B</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">the work of Whorf</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">D段, “Everett’s findings among the Pirahã have brought new life to a controversial theory by the linguist Benjamin Whorf, who suggested that people are only capable of constructing thoughts for which they possess actual words.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到Whorf的理论可能得到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Everett</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">关于Pirahã语言研究发现的支持。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p>have brought new life=be supported</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">31</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The writer refers to the Warlpiri people in order to</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> suggest that the Pirahã be taught to count in English.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> show how tribal peoples learnt a foreign language.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> compare counting in English and Portuguese.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> illustrate the uniqueness of the Pirahã.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. illustrate the uniqueness of the Pirahã.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q31, D</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Warlpiri people</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">E段, “However,the Warlpiri people had no difficulty counting farther than three in a foreign language, ...”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">提到了Warlpiri语和</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Pirahã</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">语相似，但是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Warlpiri</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">人拥有非常基本的计数系统。Warlpiri人通过学习可以掌握用英语计数，但是Pirahã人难以掌握用葡萄牙语计数。文章通过比较二者来说明上一段最后一句所提到的观点：Pirahã人无法理解算数的概念</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">32</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>What is Everett</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>s point about the Pirahã</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>s intellectual capacities?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Pirahã students have not graduated from universities.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> He does not want people to criticise their intelligence.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Their isolation makes it difficult to evaluate their intelligence.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> He believes their language is more complex than their neighbours’.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. He does not want people to criticise their intelligence.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>Q32, B</p><p>定位关键词：</p><p>intellectual capacities</p><p><br></p><p>原文：</p><p>F段, “Everett is at pains to point out that the Pirahã are not unintelligent, for their thinking is not any slower than that of the average university student...”</p><p><br></p><p>解析：</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">原文提到Everett认为Pirahã无法掌握用葡萄牙语数数并不是因为并非不聪明，相反他们的思维并不比一般大学生慢。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 33 – 36</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Complete the summary using the list of words. Write the correct letter in each gap.</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> present</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> past</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> time</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> future</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> culture</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> grammar</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>G.</strong> art</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>H.</strong> individuality</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>I.</strong> children</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">33</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong>Everett's explanation</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p>Everett believes that a group’s language is a product of their <strong><span class=\"input-blank\">________</span> </strong>and thus language is infinitely varied. During the time he spent living among them, he observed that the Pirahã only place value on the <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span> and have no <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span> to describe completed events. Similarly, the types of names they use reflect the fact that they do not celebrate <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span>.</p><p><br></p><table><tbody><tr><td data-row=\"1\">A present</td><td data-row=\"1\">B past</td><td data-row=\"1\">C time</td></tr><tr><td data-row=\"2\">D future</td><td data-row=\"2\">E culture</td><td data-row=\"2\">F grammar</td></tr><tr><td data-row=\"3\">G art</td><td data-row=\"3\">H individuality</td><td data-row=\"3\">I children</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> present</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> past</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> time</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> future</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_E\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"E\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_E\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>E.</strong> culture</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_F\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"F\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_F\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>F.</strong> grammar</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_G\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"G\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_G\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>G.</strong> art</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_H\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"H\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_H\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>H.</strong> individuality</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_I\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"I\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_I\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>I.</strong> children</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">33</span> E. culture&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">34</span> A. present&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">35</span> F. grammar&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">36</span> H. individuality</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>Q33, E</p><p>定位关键词：</p><p>language</p><p><br></p><p>原文：</p><p>E段, “Language, he believes, is created by a people’s way of life, their belief system and values. In this way, variety in human language is almost limitless, a function of the human capacity to live in different ways, such as in the forest.”</p><p><br></p><p>解析：</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">原文提到语言是由一个人的生活方式、信仰体系和价值观所创造的，</span>语言是文化的一种产品，并因此语言具有无限的变异性。</p><p><br></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>variety is limitless=infinitely varied</p><p><br></p><p>Q34, A</p><p>定位关键词：</p><p>value</p><p><br></p><p>原文：</p><p>G段，“What Everett’s research has revealed is that the central tenet of the Pirahã culture is to live in the here and now. The only thing of importance that is worth communicating to others is what is being experienced at that very moment...”</p><p><br></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到提到Pirahã语言没有过去时和未来时，只描述当前正在发生的事情。</p><p><br></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>value=tenet, worth</p><p>present=now, at that moment</p><p><br></p><p>Q35, F</p><p>定位关键词：</p><p>no, completed event</p><p><br></p><p>原文：</p><p>G段，“The only thing of importance that is worth communicating to others is what is being experienced at that very moment, though this can often be described with great care and detail. In consequence, the language has no means to conjugate verbs in order to describe ‘yesterday’ or ‘last week’ or ‘when I was a child’.”</p><p><br></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到提到Pirahã语言无法表示过去时态。</p><p><br></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>no means to conjugate verbs=grammar</p><p><br></p><p>Q36, H</p><p>定位关键词：</p><p>names</p><p><br></p><p>原文：</p><p>G段，“Standing out or being different is not encouraged by the Pirahã, and this is reflected in their perhaps colourless choice of names.”</p><p><br></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到Pirahã人的传统是给孩子取的名字没有什么想象力，通常会用部落中其他成员的名字来命名，以反映相似的性格特征，说明这些名字的类型不注重个性</p><p><br></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>Standing out or being different=individuality</p><p>is not encouraged=not celebrate</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><strong>Questions 37 – 40</strong></p><p>Choose <strong>YES </strong>if the statement agrees with the claims of the writer, choose <strong>NO </strong>if the statement contradicts the claims of the writer, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN </strong>if it is impossible to say what the writer thinks about this.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">37</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Everett was surprised by the way his research was greeted.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. NO</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q37, NO</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">the way of research was greeted</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">H段，\"Everett anticipated that these findings would be controversial and the reaction came as expected.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">anticipated, expected是surprise的反义词</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">38</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Chomsky has been critical of Everett</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>s research methodology.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Q38，NOT GIVEN</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Chomsky</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">H段, “</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Until this point, many linguists had defended the theories of Noam Chomsky, according to which all human languages have a universal grammar.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到支持</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Chomsky</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">理论的语言学家反对</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">verett观点。但是没有提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Chomsky</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">对于</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">verett研究方法论的批判。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">39</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>If </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>‘</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>recursion</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> as a universal concept is disproved, Chomsky</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>s ideas about language would be wrong.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Q39，YES</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">recursion</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">H段，“And, most pertinent to Everett’s work, there would not be subordinate clauses, which are responsible for translating the concept of recursion into grammar. But if the Pirahã do not form subordinate clauses, then recursion cannot explain the uniqueness of human language, and this would negate Chomsky’s theories.”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到recursion是</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Chomsky</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">语言理论的核心概念，并指出该概念被推翻会对</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Chomsky</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">的理论造成重大挑战。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><br></p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">40</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The Pirahã will benefit from their new-found status among academics.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. NO</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Q40， NO</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">benefit, new found status</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">I段，”</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">My concern is that soon the Pirahã will simply become one more scientific oddity with every aspect of their lives being exploited and analysed.“</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">文章提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Everett</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">担心Pirahã会被当做怪人怪事来进行研究分析这与题目中Pirahã将会从其在学术领域的新地位获得好处相矛盾。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>",
